name: LetsBeReal
description:
LetsBeReal is a perfect merge of Clarity (v2), Deliberate (v2), and Realistic Vision (v2) with a splash of my own specially trained base model from a collection of real females with better makeup and hairstyles.

I wasn't sure what the best category was merged or trained since it was both, so I put "merge" just to be safe.

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description: This model is a merge of deliberate, clarity and realistic vision at heart, so any of the keywords used for those should work for this as well. As far as the other base model I trained, I simply used the keyword "woman".
